name: View the loyalty point on Receipt

steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I clock in the timesheet with PIN "2883"
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('2', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('8', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('8', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('3', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'CONFIRM', exact: true })
Then I should see the employee "Gabriella" in the employee list
And I add the "Manicure" service to my cart
Then I should see my cart showing 1 item added
When I click on the total price of "Manicure"
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
Click locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
When I select the service "Manicure" in my cart
And I select the "DISCOUNT ITEM" on the menu
Then I should see the "Original Price (Owner)" option is active
When I select the discount "Open Discount"
Then I should see the "Amount" discount type is active
And I click on the "OK" button
Then I should see the "Open Discount (Original Price)" discount in my cart
And I should see discount "($3.00)" in my cart
When I click on the adding "Discount" button
Then I should see the "Original Price (Owner)" option is active
When I select the discount absorb type "Discounted Price (Technician)"
Then I should see the "Discounted Price (Technician)" option is active
When I select the discount "Open Discount"
And I select the "Percent" discount type
Then I should see the "Percent" discount type is active
And I click on the "OK" button
Then I should see the discount ticket detail "Open Discount 10% (Discounted Price)($3.25)" in my cart
And I should see "Discount ($3.25)" in my cart
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('ul.xCharge li').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'Discount' }) })
Expect "toHaveText" locator('ul.xCharge li').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'Discount' }) }).locator('span').first()
Expect "toContainText" locator('ul.xCharge li').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'Discount' }) }).locator('span').nth(1)
When I click to create new customer with the default loyalty program "2 Points = $1"
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Click Here To Add Customers', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Click Here To Add Customers', exact: true })
Wait for selector locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
And I create the new customer name "Loyalty"
Wait for selector locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })

Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'Save', exact: true })

Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'Save', exact: true })
Expect "not toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
When I click on the "Pay" button
And I select the "Cash" payment type
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Close Ticket"
And I should see a popup dialog with content "CHANGE$70.75OK"
When I click on the "OK" button in the popup dialog
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
When I select the "CLOSED TICKET" tab
Then I should see the toast message "Ticket data refreshed successfully." visible
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.MuiAlert-message').filter({ hasText: 'Ticket data refreshed successfully.' })
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the first ticket of payment "$29.25"
When I click on the first row for payment "$29.25"
Then I should see the store logo on the receipt
And I should see the business info "PINK SALON 1032 YONKERS AVE Yonkers Avenel, NJ 07001 (090) 123-4567" on the receipt
Then I should see the date is today on the receipt
And I should see the customer name "Loyalty" on the receipt
And I should see the point "58 = $0.58" on the receipt
Then I should see the service quantity "1" on the receipt

Expect "toHaveText" locator('.render-bill div[style*="margin-top: 16px;"]').filter({ has: locator('div').filter({ hasText: 'Item Name' }) }).first().locator('div[style*="display: flex; flex-direction: row;"]').last().locator('div').first()
And I should see the service name "Manicure" on the receipt

Expect "toHaveText" locator('.render-bill div[style*="margin-top: 16px;"]').filter({ has: locator('div').filter({ hasText: 'Item Name' }) }).first().locator('div[style*="display: flex; flex-direction: row;"]').last().locator('div').nth(1)
And I should see the technician name "Gabriella" on the receipt

Expect "toHaveText" locator('.render-bill div[style*="margin-top: 16px;"]').filter({ has: locator('div').filter({ hasText: 'Item Name' }) }).first().locator('div[style*="display: flex; flex-direction: row;"]').last().locator('div').nth(2)
And I should see the service price "$35.50" on the receipt

Expect "toHaveText" locator('.render-bill div[style*="margin-top: 16px;"]').filter({ has: locator('div').filter({ hasText: 'Item Name' }) }).first().locator('div[style*="display: flex; flex-direction: row;"]').last().locator('div').nth(3)
And I should see the discount item name "Open Discount" on the receipt
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[style*="justify-content: space-between"]').filter({ hasText: 'Open Discount' }).locator('div').filter({ hasText: 'Open Discount' })
And I should see the discount item amount "($3.00)" on the receipt
Then I should see the discount ticket name "Open Discount" on the receipt
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('table tr').filter({ has: locator('td').filter({ hasText: 'Open Discount' }) })
Expect "toHaveText" locator('table tr').filter({ has: locator('td').filter({ hasText: 'Open Discount' }) }).locator('td').nth(1)
And I should see the discount ticket amount "($3.25)" on the receipt
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('table tr').filter({ has: locator('td').filter({ hasText: '($3.25)' }) })
Expect "toHaveText" locator('table tr').filter({ has: locator('td').filter({ hasText: '($3.25)' }) }).locator('td').last()
And I should see the TIP amount "$0.00" on the receipt
And I should see the SUBTOTAL "$29.25" on the receipt
And I should see the TAX "$0.00" on the receipt
And I should see the TOTAL "$29.25" on the receipt
Then I should see the CHANGE amount "$70.75" on the receipt
Then I should see the payment label "PAYMENT DETAILS" on the receipt
And I should see the payment method "Cash - $100.00" on the receipt
And I should see the cash payment amount "$29.25" on the receipt
Then I should see the message "Come back again soon..." on the receipt
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.render-bill').filter({ hasText: 'Come back again soon...' })
And I should see the message "Thank you <3" on the receipt
Then I should see the tip guide "10% TIP = $2.92" on the receipt
And I should see the tip guide "15% TIP = $4.39" on the receipt
And I should see the tip guide "20% TIP = $5.85" on the receipt
Then I should see the QR code on the receipt
